# PR & Commits

## Commit Message Template
```
feat(scope): short summary
- change 1
- change 2
Tests: added/updated
Docs: updated
Refs: issues/links
```

## PR Checklist
- [ ] Builds and lints clean
- [ ] Backward compatible or migration documented
- [ ] Tests added/updated (unit/integration/regression)
- [ ] Docs/CHANGELOG updated with references
- [ ] Perf and security considered
- [ ] Evidence block present and valid
- [ ] Rollback plan or feature flag if risky

## Review Rules
- Explain “why”, not only “what”.
- Link to ADR or create/update one if architecture changed.
